  "title": {
    "zh": "储能器与燃油",
    "en": "Energy store and fuel"
  },
  "summary": {
    "zh": "混合动力 F1 的电池储能器（ES）受 4MJ 单圈能量差上限约束，是重量、安全与功率的精密折中；燃油则按流量上限配给，每一滴都要压榨出最大热值。",
    "en": "The hybrid-era Energy Store (ES) is capped to a 4MJ-per-lap energy delta, a precise trade of mass, safety and power; fuel is metered by a flow limit, every drop wrung for maximum calorific value."
  },
  "sourceIds": ["source-book-f1-illustrated-engineering"],
